Herod

Herod Agrippa I, grandson of Herod the Great,

(See Scofield) - ([Mat 2:1](../../../bib/kjv/mat002.htm#001).md),

a strict observer of the law, and popular with the Jews, see ([Act
12:21](../../../bib/kjv/act012.htm#021).md).

Herod Agrippa II, Paul's Agrippa, was his son.

